# Squirrel — Cursor Rules

## What this plugin does

squirrel keeps cognitive state across sessions. It stores progress, open
questions, blockers, and next actions in a Markdown vault so that returning to
a project doesn't require re-reading 20 files.

## Skill index

Skills live at `~/.cursor/rules/squirrel/`. Load the relevant SKILL.md
when the user's request matches the trigger.

| Skill | Trigger | SKILL.md |
|---|---|---|
| `session-start` | "vamos a retomar X", "what was I doing", "load context" | `session-start/SKILL.md` |
| `session-end` | "cerramos", "shutdown", "pausing for today" | `session-end/SKILL.md` |
| `brief` | "dame el brief", "status update", "summarize project" | `brief/SKILL.md` |
| `capture` | "save this", "anotá", "guardá" | `capture/SKILL.md` |
| `decision` | "decidimos", "we're going with", "record this decision" | `decision/SKILL.md` |
| `where-am-i` | "where am I", "¿en qué estoy?", "focus snapshot" | `where-am-i/SKILL.md` |
| `sync-out` | "export context", "necesito llevar esto" | `sync-out/SKILL.md` |
| `sync-in` | user pastes a `<!-- CONTEXT-BRIDGE-PACKAGE` block | `sync-in/SKILL.md` |
| `chunk-intent` | "break this intent into chunks" | `chunk-intent/SKILL.md` |
| `task-initiation` | "can't start", "paralyzed", "stuck" | `task-initiation/SKILL.md` |
| `parakeet` | "what are my deadlines" | `parakeet/SKILL.md` |
| `hyperfocus-guardian` | session running >2h or user drifting from original intent | `hyperfocus-guardian/SKILL.md` |

## Configuration

`~/.squirrel/config.toml` must exist before skills work. Minimum:

```toml
vault_path = "~/vault-tdah"
environment_name = "personal"
```

Run `sq install --agent cursor` from the squirrel repo to set up skills.
Run `python3 /path/to/squirrel/lib/status_aggregator.py --vault ~/vault-tdah --pretty`
to verify vault connectivity.

## Vault conventions

```
vault/
  01-Proyectos-Activos/<PROJECT>/
    <PROJECT>.md        # Project Page — goal, DoD, stakeholders
    <PROJECT>-<TAG>.md  # Intent files — tasks, shutdown notes
  02-Parking-Lot/       # Paused projects
  03-Areas/             # Recurring responsibilities
  06-Archive/           # Completed projects
  99-Resources/         # Reference material, inbox
```

Intent frontmatter format:

```yaml
---
id: TAG-NAME
tipo: A|B|C
estado: pending|in-progress|blocked|done
prioridad: normal|high|finishing-tax
deadline: 2026-06-01
---
```

## Scripts (stdlib Python 3.9+, no pip required)

Run directly or invoke from skills:

```bash
python3 lib/status_aggregator.py --vault ~/vault-tdah --pretty
python3 lib/deadline_scanner.py --vault ~/vault-tdah --level critical,urgent
python3 lib/estimate_buffer.py --hours 3
python3 lib/chunk_helper.py --hours 8 --pretty
```

## CLI

```bash
cb status          # vault health
cb deadlines       # urgency-sorted deadlines
cb chunk --hours 4 # ADHD-friendly decomposition
cb estimate --hours 2
cb install --agent cursor --dry-run
```
